How to Compile:

(in Linux from terminal)


From terminal opened in Here:

g++ -I/PATH/opencvnew/Here -L/PATH/opencvnew/mylib/ -g -o headV HeadPoseVtry.cpp faceDetect.cpp -lopencv_core -lopencv_imgcodecs -lopencv_imgproc -lopencv_highgui -lopencv_ml -lopencv_video -lopencv_videoio -lopencv_videostab -lopencv_features2d -lopencv_calib3d -lopencv_objdetect


Functional example:

g++ -I/home/georgette/Desktop/opencvnew/Here -L/home/georgette/Desktop/opencvnew/mylib/ -g -o headV HeadPoseVtry.cpp faceDetect.cpp -lopencv_core -lopencv_imgcodecs -lopencv_imgproc -lopencv_highgui -lopencv_ml -lopencv_video -lopencv_videoio -lopencv_videostab -lopencv_features2d -lopencv_calib3d -lopencv_objdetect*

*/home/georgette/Desktop/ = PATH -->substitute with the path where you saved opencvnew

